  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/682df4518c56886f869dfbdd03e98367.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/682df4518c56886f869dfbdd03e98367.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/682df4518c56886f869dfbdd03e98367.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⛵ Set Sail for Adventure</strong></h2>  <br>Start your fishing journey from scratch in the middle of the ocean! Set sail with your boat, catch fish, sell them, and upgrade both yourself and your fleet. Each day brings you closer to building your fishing empire!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/4556f264527b56c49897988098edcbff.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/4556f264527b56c49897988098edcbff.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/4556f264527b56c49897988098edcbff.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚤 15+ Ships Await You</strong></h2>  <br>Begin with a small boat and progress to powerful, impressive ships! Discover over 15 ships with unique designs, speeds, and capacities. Bigger ships mean faster fishing, more profits, and domination over the seas!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/10c58384cde39dcc404ff26f735b5551.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/10c58384cde39dcc404ff26f735b5551.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/10c58384cde39dcc404ff26f735b5551.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💸 Profitable Auctions</strong></h2>  <br>Fishing isn’t just about catching! Sell your fish wisely and grow your economy. With the auction system, follow market trends and sell at the best prices. Make strategic moves and watch your fortune grow timing is everything!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/709cb25d264b2db3e1d2cd94a9993187.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/709cb25d264b2db3e1d2cd94a9993187.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/709cb25d264b2db3e1d2cd94a9993187.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌅 Relax with Cozy Graphics</strong></h2>  <br>Get ready for a peaceful fishing experience away from intense action. Fisher Idle offers a calm, cozy atmosphere to melt your stress away. Enjoy fishing with colorful islands, soothing ocean views, and relaxing visuals!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/d829369d7e47a80301ffac86833fd6be.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 Fisher Idle Features</strong></h2>  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 15 Advanced Ships with Unique Features<br></li><li>Unlock New Ships and Perks with the XP System<br></li><li>Custom Upgrade Mechanics for Each Ship<br></li><li>Dynamic Economy Management with Auctions<br></li><li>Hire Fishermen for Automated Fishing<br></li><li>Upgrade Your Hired Fishermen to Boost Income<br></li><li>Fun and Surprise-Filled Mini Games<br></li><li>Expand to the Global Market with the Trade Castle (In Development!)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/682df4518c56886f869dfbdd03e98367.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/682df4518c56886f869dfbdd03e98367.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/682df4518c56886f869dfbdd03e98367.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⛵ Set Sail for Adventure</strong></h2>  <br>Start your fishing journey from scratch in the middle of the ocean! Set sail with your boat, catch fish, sell them, and upgrade both yourself and your fleet. Each day brings you closer to building your fishing empire!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/4556f264527b56c49897988098edcbff.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/4556f264527b56c49897988098edcbff.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/4556f264527b56c49897988098edcbff.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚤 15+ Ships Await You</strong></h2>  <br>Begin with a small boat and progress to powerful, impressive ships! Discover over 15 ships with unique designs, speeds, and capacities. Bigger ships mean faster fishing, more profits, and domination over the seas!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/10c58384cde39dcc404ff26f735b5551.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/10c58384cde39dcc404ff26f735b5551.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/10c58384cde39dcc404ff26f735b5551.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💸 Profitable Auctions</strong></h2>  <br>Fishing isn’t just about catching! Sell your fish wisely and grow your economy. With the auction system, follow market trends and sell at the best prices. Make strategic moves and watch your fortune grow timing is everything!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/709cb25d264b2db3e1d2cd94a9993187.poster.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/709cb25d264b2db3e1d2cd94a9993187.webm?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/709cb25d264b2db3e1d2cd94a9993187.mp4?t=1750009114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌅 Relax with Cozy Graphics</strong></h2>  <br>Get ready for a peaceful fishing experience away from intense action. Fisher Idle offers a calm, cozy atmosphere to melt your stress away. Enjoy fishing with colorful islands, soothing ocean views, and relaxing visuals!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449840/extras/d829369d7e47a80301ffac86833fd6be.avif?t=1750009114\" width=610 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 Fisher Idle Features</strong></h2>  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 15 Advanced Ships with Unique Features<br></li><li>Unlock New Ships and Perks with the XP System<br></li><li>Custom Upgrade Mechanics for Each Ship<br></li><li>Dynamic Economy Management with Auctions<br></li><li>Hire Fishermen for Automated Fishing<br></li><li>Upgrade Your Hired Fishermen to Boost Income<br></li><li>Fun and Surprise-Filled Mini Games<br></li><li>Expand to the Global Market with the Trade Castle (In Development!)</li></ul>",
